// Crisis management | Crisis Ministry
// Youth Affairs, Sports Intra-Alär Tourism, Arts and Tourism | Culture Ministry
// Economic Democracy, Subsidies, Monetary Policy | Economic Ministry
// Education & Health & Miscellaneous Regulations (Food, Consumer Protections) | Education & Health Ministry
// Scienc, Green, Technology | Environment and Technology Ministry
// Taxes | Fiscal Ministry
// Interior & Drugs | Interior Ministry
// Judiciary, Constitution & Executive Rights | Judiciary
// Military Policy | Military Ministry
// Postal Service | Postal Ministry 
// Communications & Internet | Public Communications Ministry
// Utilities - Energy, Water, Telephone/Wifi | Public Utilities Ministry
